            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2018-10-24T10:40:23.000+01:00">24 October 2018</time>
              Removed link to 'Estimates of the separated family population' (section 4.2). The process of refreshing this indicator has revealed significant issues with its methodology. We are currently developing a new indicator.
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2018-10-19T12:04:00.000+01:00">19 October 2018</time>
              Changed title of indicator 'Children benefitting from a child maintenance arrangement' to 'Percentage of separated families with a child maintenance arrangement' (section 4.2).
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2018-06-29T10:14:40.000+01:00">29 June 2018</time>
              Added technical annex showing how DWP calculates the headline indicators that demonstrate progress against its strategic objectives.
            </li>
